QuestData.Title: The Dark Side of the Moon
QuestData.Description: Yrel and I have located Warlord Ner'zhul. He is meeting with Grommash Hellscream atop the highest altar overlooking Anguish Fortress.$B$BMeet us there. We must stop him.

Objectives.Objective: Find Velen and Yrel at the Terrace of the Stars
